headline: CME Group Announces 100 Million Event Contracts Traded
summary: CME Group, the world's leading derivatives marketplace, today announced its event contracts reached a new milestone of 100 million contracts traded since launch in December.

headline: CME Group Expands Futures Suite With Rare Earths And Single Stock Contracts
summary: CME Group is launching what it describes as the world's first rare earths futures contract, targeting neodymium and praseodymium. The company is also introducing single stock futures on more than 50 large cap U.S. equities. These products aim to expand CME Group's derivatives offering for both commodity and equity markets.
